com.citi.get.common.data.lookup.dna.DNAL.name: lookup_dna_db_init_equity
com.citi.get.common.data.lookup.dna.DNAL.query: set nocount on;execute GetProduct @filter_sql='select distinct o.SMCP,o.MarketSectorDescription from OCEAN_SMCP_DATA_SOURCESYS o WITH(NOLOCK) inner join PRODUCT p WITH(NOLOCK) on p.SMCP=o.SMCP where p.OperationalIndicator=''Y'' and (p.IsDummyProduct=''N'' or p.IsDummyProduct is null) and o.SOURCE_SYS=''UKLQFI'' and o.MarketSectorDescription not in(''FUTURE'',''OPTION'') and o.TRADE_DATE > GETDATE()-60'
